Name:           php-phpspec-prophecy
Version:        1.20.0
Release:        1%{?dist}
Summary:        Highly opinionated mocking framework for PHP

License:        MIT
URL:            https://github.com/%{gh_owner}/%{gh_project}
Source0:        %{name}-%{version}-%{gh_short}.tgz
